premise_source_doc_sentence: Dhoom 3  (  -LSB- - hnsˈd̪ʱuːm 3 -RSB- , English : Blast 3 or Boom 3 , also abbreviated and known as D :3 and D3  )  is a 2013 Indian action thriller film written and directed by Vijay Krishna Acharya and produced by Aditya Chopra .

Dhoom 2  (  -LSB- - hnsˈd̪ʱuːm -RSB- , English : Blast 2 , also abbreviated and known as D :2 , D2 and Dhoom 2 : Back In Action  )  is a 2006 Indian action film directed by Sanjay Gadhvi and produced by Aditya Chopra and Yash Chopra at an estimated budget of under the Yash Raj Films banner .
